c0000493
00:19:17.620 --> 00:19:19.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after Sakurajima dumped you.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:19:19.370 --> 00:19:21.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The three of us already know
Tomoe's cute,</b></Default>

c0000495
00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but what else
is it you like about her?</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:23.950 --> 00:19:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think there's some kind
of misunderstanding.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:26.500 --> 00:19:28.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's obvious you like her
so there's no need to hide it.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:28.960 --> 00:19:31.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I see Tomoe.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:31.550 --> 00:19:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all giggling]</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:33.050 --> 00:19:34.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, my gosh, you guys!</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:36.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really came all this way
to see me?</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:36.590 --> 00:19:38.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I told you we would
come visit you.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:38.180 --> 00:19:40.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Such a cute uniform.
- Yeah, it's adorable.</b></Default>

c0000504
00:19:40.890 --> 00:19:42.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Listen.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:19:42.140 --> 00:19:43.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're just toying
with Tomoe,</b></Default>

c0000506
00:19:43.430 --> 00:19:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't forgive you.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:19:45.230 --> 00:19:46.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:19:53.360 --> 00:19:54.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, wait!</b></Default>

c0000509
00:19:54.740 --> 00:19:56.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a favor to ask you.
- No, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:19:56.740 --> 00:19:58.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The least you could do
is hear me out.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:19:58.410 --> 00:19:59.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not interested. Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:19:59.570 --> 00:20:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But why not?
- Let me guess.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:01.490 --> 00:20:03.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People think the two of us
are currently dating</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:03.740 --> 00:20:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you'd like me
to keep pretending we are.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I didn't know you had
the power to read minds.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:08.080 --> 00:20:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Come on. There's other things
to worry about.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:10.580 --> 00:20:12.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like puberty syndrome,
for example.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:12.670 --> 00:20:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's not an issue 'cause
we moved onto today, right?</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:15.130 --> 00:20:16.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no time to think
about that, anyway!</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:16.840 --> 00:20:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm in trouble!</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:17.880 --> 00:20:18.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How long do you plan on</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:18.930 --> 00:20:19.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>letting people think that you</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:19.930 --> 00:20:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I are dating?</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:21.390 --> 00:20:23.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't tell me till
the third-years graduate.</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:23.470 --> 00:20:25.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I've already thought
that part out. I promise.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:26.020 --> 00:20:28.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm only asking to pretend
for the rest of the first term.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:28.520 --> 00:20:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So please!</b></Default>

c0000528
00:20:29.650 --> 00:20:30.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once it's summer break,</b></Default>

c0000529
00:20:30.770 --> 00:20:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we won't have classes.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:20:32.270 --> 00:20:34.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can say our relationship
started fizzling out</b></Default>

c0000531
00:20:34.650 --> 00:20:36.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and then we can go into
the second term like normal.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:20:37.490 --> 00:20:38.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000533
00:20:39.490 --> 00:20:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Come on!
It's not that big a deal!</b></Default>

c0000534
00:20:43.830 --> 00:20:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I hate to say this
