c0000537
00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Actually, your reputation's
not as bad as you think anymore</b></Default>

c0000538
00:20:53.840 --> 00:20:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since all the first-years accept
you now,</b></Default>

c0000539
00:20:55.550 --> 00:20:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I think it should be fine.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:20:56.670 --> 00:20:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's that about?</b></Default>

c0000541
00:20:58.260 --> 00:21:00.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Loudly confessing your love
at school is usually seen</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:00.840 --> 00:21:03.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as crazy but some people totally
admired you for ti.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:03.720 --> 00:21:05.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'd never do that for you,
you know.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:08.060 --> 00:21:09.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, that's right!</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:09.480 --> 00:21:11.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's too sudden
if we're already dating.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:11.440 --> 00:21:13.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's try something
one step before that.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:13.560 --> 00:21:15.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?
- Yeah, like we're not quite</b></Default>

c0000549
00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:16.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>dating yet,
but we're close.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:21:16.610 --> 00:21:17.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Koga.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:21:17.940 --> 00:21:19.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know what you're about</b></Default>

c0000552
00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:20.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to do by going through
with this?</b></Default>

c0000553
00:21:20.990 --> 00:21:23.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna be telling a lie
to the entire school.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:25.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I already know
the consequences.</b></Default>

c0000555
00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:26.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000556
00:21:27.330 --> 00:21:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000557
00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:32.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I moved from Fukuoka
after middle school.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:36.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I only have friends I've made
while attending Minegahara.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:21:36.630 --> 00:21:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean those three earlier?</b></Default>

c0000560
00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:40.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right, but at this rate,</b></Default>

c0000561
00:21:40.470 --> 00:21:42.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't have a place in class
