c0000562
00:21:43.300 --> 00:21:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be spending my break alone,
eating lunch at a table alone,</b></Default>

c0000563
00:21:46.890 --> 00:21:48.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and going to the bathroom alone.</b></Default>

c0000564
00:21:48.970 --> 00:21:50.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At least go
to the bathroom alone.</b></Default>

c0000565
00:21:50.350 --> 00:21:51.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nuh-uh.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:21:51.600 --> 00:21:53.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Being alone is easy in
