c0000568
00:21:56.190 --> 00:21:58.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's really not as lonely
as you'd expect it to be.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:21:59.030 --> 00:22:01.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- None of this is 'cause I think
I'm gonna feel lonely.</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:01.820 --> 00:22:03.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Well then, why?</b></Default>

c0000571
00:22:05.620 --> 00:22:06.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Being alone is...</b></Default>

c0000572
00:22:07.540 --> 00:22:09.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Embarrassing.</b></Default>

c0000573
00:22:09.950 --> 00:22:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want people to think
I'm always by myself.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:22:13.420 --> 00:22:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't.</b></Default>

c0000575
00:22:15.040 --> 00:22:16.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:22:17.340 --> 00:22:18.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Going to school is...</b></Default>

c0000577
00:22:19.380 --> 00:22:21.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Embarrassing.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:22:21.590 --> 00:22:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000579
00:22:23.050 --> 00:22:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000580
00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:26.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Something wrong?
- Fine, then.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:22:27.390 --> 00:22:29.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna help you lie
to the entire school.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:22:29.680 --> 00:22:31.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You will?
- Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000583
00:22:31.680 --> 00:22:33.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Also, another favor.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:22:33.640 --> 00:22:35.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It--it's about tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:22:35.600 --> 00:22:37.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After your shift is over,</b></Default>

c0000586
00:22:37.520 --> 00:22:40.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can I maybe g--g--g--</b></Default>

c0000587
00:22:40.730 --> 00:22:42.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Get a forehead flick?
- No!</b></Default>

c0000588
00:22:42.740 --> 00:22:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go on a date!</b></Default>

c0000589
00:22:44.490 --> 00:22:46.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]
A date?</b></Default>

c0000590
00:22:47.320 --> 00:22:50.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Rena asked me if I was going
to go on dates with you.</b></Default>

c0000591
00:22:50.950 --> 00:22:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You just lie and say,</b></Default>

c0000592
00:22:52.450 --> 00:22:54.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Yeah, we had so much fun
this weekend,"</b></Default>

c0000593
00:22:54.620 --> 00:22:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or something like that,
couldn't you?</b></Default>

c0000594
00:22:56.330 --> 00:22:58.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But I want photo evidence just
in case.</b></Default>

c0000595
00:22:58.670 --> 00:23:00.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're surprisingly cautious,
aren't you, Koga?</b></Default>

c0000596
00:23:02.630 --> 00:23:05.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How am I supposed to tell Mai
