c0000597
00:23:05.930 --> 00:23:07.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet she'll watch
as I desperately try</b></Default>

c0000598
00:23:07.930 --> 00:23:10.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to explain things and she'll
be smiling the whole time.</b></Default>

c0000599
00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:17.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dang it.
She's gonna have a field day.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:23:18.730 --> 00:23:20.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> - This is the last week of Jun.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:23:20.230 --> 00:23:21.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b> Prepare for much warmer weathe.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:23:22.070 --> 00:23:24.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our meteorologist Sakiyama
will have a forecast</b></Default>

c0000603
00:23:25.030 --> 00:23:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you coming up soon.</b></Default>

c0000604
00:23:26.990 --> 00:23:28.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wait a sec!
Big brother, lookit!</b></Default>

c0000605
00:23:29.070 --> 00:23:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Isn't that the girl you brought
over here the other day?</b></Default>

c0000606
00:23:32.290 --> 00:23:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, do you want a sip?</b></Default>

c0000607
00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]
Nuh-uh! It's all mine!</b></Default>

c0000608
00:23:36.710 --> 00:23:38.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-huh.
Yeah, that's her.</b></Default>

c0000609
00:23:38.210 --> 00:23:39.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell rings]</b></Default>

c0000610
00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh, who's coming by this late
