c0000611
00:23:42.800 --> 00:23:43.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes?</b></Default>

c0000612
00:23:44.340 --> 00:23:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, it's me.</b></Default>

